A library for doing some basic text analysis and statistics.
Includes functionality for:
- Detecting the language of the text (using language-detection library
from https://code.google.com/p/language-detection/). /res directory
contains the necessary language profiles for the library
- Calculating statistics for English texts, including the word count,
syllable count, polysyllable word count, sentence count and
Flesch-Kincaid readability index for the text
- An implementation of TextRank algorithm for automatic text
summarization and simple keyword extraction. Algorithm is presented
in http://acl.ldc.upenn.edu/acl2004/emnlp/pdf/Mihalcea.pdf
